# Getting started

## Get the things ready

```
johndoe@foobar:~# dnf install docker podman
johndoe@foobar:~# git clone https://github.com/xroumegue/yocto-builder.git
johndoe@foobar:~# cd yocto-builder
johndoe@foobar:yocto-builder# git submodule update --init 
```

## Build a platform

```
johndoe@foobar:yocto-builder# ./build.sh build configs/genericarm64.yaml
```

